# Per-VIN factory option (FA / SA) dump.
#
# Format: VIN | sa1,sa2,sa3 | paintCode | upholsteryCode | YYYY-MM
#
# Sourced from BMW PartsLink24 FA exports (one VIN per line). Loaded on
# server boot by `server/etk-vin-fa.ts`; can also be re-imported on
# demand via `npx tsx scripts/import-vin-fa-dump.ts`. Comment lines
# (prefixed with `#`) and blank lines are ignored.
#
# Source-priority on conflict (preserved by the loader):
#   etk_fa_import (admin HTTP) > etk_fa_dump (this file)
#                              > promoted_from_cache > e2e_fixture
#
# The first row below is the deterministic E2E fixture VIN that the
# verify-vin-enrichment test suite asserts against — keep it present
# (or override via an etk_fa_import row) so the strict first-party
# regime can be regression-tested without touching bimmer.work.
WBS32AY090FM28236|S206,S2VB,S2TB|475|FAAT|2020-09
